result.title: Radyo5 101.9 News FM - DYNC
result.description:
DYNC, under the brand WAV 1019, is a music FM radio station owned by tion Broadcasting Corporation and operated by audioWAV Productions in the Philippines. The station's studio is located in Lahug, Cebu City.
The station was previously known as 101.9 Charlie, they played pop jazz, retro, and easy listening.

On October 1, 2009, audioWAV and NBC (through its parent MediaQuest) relaunched both Cebu and Davao stations as CHR-formatted WAV FM.

Soon, audioWAV will be reformatted as Radyo5, the first FM station in the Philippines that delivers news and information.
